# LuiAchieve bootstrap

This repo is **LuiAchieve**, a **Playnite extension** (C#, .NET Framework 4.6.2, WPF).

Before non-trivial edits, read **AGENTS.md** at the repository root: architecture, threading/WPF rules, C# conventions, build/test, and the **code review checklist** (functionality through documentation).

If the user attaches `@AGENTS.md`, treat it as the source of truth for architecture and standards.
